{"tid":284563,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV昨日於將軍澳舉行劇集《詭探》祝捷會","createTime":"2017-06-15T04:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T11:46:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e420ae3b6a5a931319981187bf4bb8d500c9c3","tid":284563,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20056016&amp;category_guid=462&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20056016%26category_guid%3D462%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170615&d=726XWuJThIpQNweI59qHvxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d7be6c85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20056016%26category_guid%3D462%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170615&h=e969e9ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20056016&amp;category_guid=462&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170615</a><br />\n<br />\n邵仲衡赴英再拍ViuTV<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n邵仲衡昨日對於《詭探》收視理想感興奮，更指將會與陳奕迅合拍新劇。<br />\n<br />\nViuTV昨日於將軍澳舉行劇集《詭探》祝捷會，演員邵仲衡、尹揚明、蔣祖曼及趙碩之等均有出席，同場宣佈ViuTV開拍另外十齣不同種類電視劇，當中有科幻劇《藍橘子》、荒誕系列《賤民20》、校園系列《教束》及音樂劇《短暫的婚姻》等。<br />\n<br />\n邵仲衡對《詭探》收視理想感到喜出望外，隨後他會參與《短暫的婚姻》演出，他說：「我唔係唱歌，會同Eason（陳奕迅）同場，佢係一個好有想法嘅歌手，到時會去英國拍外景。」蔣祖曼日前於劇中食生牛肉惹迴響，實際她是用吞拿魚代替，她說：「用生牛肉拍攝時，我問導演可唔可以舔，導演指牛肉放太耐怕唔乾淨，聞到真係好腥。」<br />\n採訪：張俊銘<br />\n攝影：陳慧安<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n蔣祖曼昨自爆在劇中食生牛肉一幕是以吞拿魚代替。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170615/large/15ec2p17e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170615%2Flarge%2F15ec2p17e.jpg&h=375a4795&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7119687145ae7363028439d7f575021720190deb","tid":284563,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:37:00.000Z","msg":"琴晚睇 viutv既 十五分鐘熱度，<br />\n<br />\n見到 Renci幾靚女，<br />\n<br />\njoman好 fit"},{"pid":"9a8cd9fe671c1f6e7b445a2d392e679678e9b756","tid":284563,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"套野拍得太差<br />\n<br />\n追咗一本放棄咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af673b6fd1e0af1a84cab8580662a78dbb47cad","tid":284563,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1kqud63r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1kqud63r&h=bd0007c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d33828861ee304ef30f4049234bd1dbcb35deec6","tid":284563,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T05:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>套野拍得太差<br />\n<br />\n追咗一本放棄咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出左書？"},{"pid":"e91b4e68246c73963ca402994f03676128e3e51a","tid":284563,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T05:55:14.000Z","msg":"一集半個鐘都冇，好似唔上唔落咁，不過都套野都ok"},{"pid":"62c445ca41481d29402141f2a676f9e197307673","tid":284563,"uid":58456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>套野拍得太差<br />\n<br />\n追咗一本放棄咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開頭個故事真心趕客<br />\n但依家講降頭好左"},{"pid":"f26bdbd69388e933d01d7b820007c0db840e541b","tid":284563,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"教束<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd592b6c5abbf09c0c801725c7b7a56edaca1730","tid":284563,"uid":20337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>套野拍得太差<br />\n<br />\n追咗一本放棄咗 <img src=\